'''Chuck Sperati''' wrote the short story "[[Droid Trouble]]" for the [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 3|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 3]] in 1994, which was later archived on [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]]. Chuck also wrote the article "[[A Deal Gone Sour]]" for [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 4|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 4]]. In addition, Chuck has written two novels, a number of short stories in various genres, and a tabletop roleplaying game called ''Legacy of Adventure''.

